# FILE: studentDashboard/financialTerminal/walletOverview.desc
# ROLE: Personal Finance & Subscription Command Center
# ROUTE: /dashboard/wallet
# ACCOUNT: Student only
# THEME: Dark · monospace data · colored status pills

## 1. CASH-FLOW SUMMARY (Top Row — 3 cards)
- CARD STYLE: bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-2xl · border · p-7 · text-center
- CARD A: Total spent (SYP) on Store + Academy — rose color
- CARD B: Freelance earnings (shown only if isFreelancer === true) — emerald color
- CARD C: Pending verification amount — amber color
- SAVINGS BADGE: "وفّرت 45,000 SYP عبر الخصومات الطلابية" — below cards

## 2. FREELANCE SUBSCRIPTION TRACKER (Conditional)
- Shown only when isFreelancer === true
- STATUS BOX: border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl
  - 🟢 Active: border-[#10B981]/30 · text-[#10B981]
  - 🔴 Expired: border-[#F43F5E]/30 · text-[#F43F5E]
- DATA: plan status · days remaining · next payment date
- ACTION: [💳 تجديد الاشتراك] → opens ShamCash payment modal

## 3. TRANSACTION HISTORY TABLE
- STYLE: bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-2xl · border · overflow-hidden
- COLUMNS: التاريخ · رقم المعاملة · الغرض · الحالة · المبلغ
- STATUS PILLS:
  - 🕒 قيد المراجعة — amber pill
  - ✅ مكتمل — emerald pill
  - ❌ مرفوض — rose pill
- PURPOSES: 🛒 متجر · 💼 اشتراك · 🎓 أكاديمية

## 4. VIRTUAL WALLET (Platform Credit)
- DISPLAY: [💰 الرصيد المتاح: 25,000 SYP]
- CARD STYLE: bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6366F1]/12 to-[#8B5CF6]/6 · rounded-2xl · border-[#6366F1]/25
- USE CASE: applied as discount on next purchase in Halab Store
- Logic: auto-credited when an order is cancelled or a dispute is won

## 5. PAYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
- ShamCash QR code display in a bordered box
- Step-by-step: Scan → Pay → Copy TX ID → Submit
- SUBMIT RECEIPT BUTTON: gradient-bg · "📤 إرسال إيصال الدفع"

## 6. EXPORT
- [📄 تحميل كشف حساب PDF] — ghost button
